# {{ project_name }}

## Project Type
Next.js (App Router) with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.

## Architecture Rules
- Use the App Router (`src/app/`) with server components by default.
- Mark client components explicitly with `"use client"`.
- API routes go in `src/app/api/`.
- Shared components in `src/components/`.
- Use TypeScript strict mode. No `any` types.

## Commands
- `npm run dev` — start dev server
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm run lint` — ESLint
- `npm test` — run tests

## Style Guide
- Tailwind CSS utility classes. No CSS modules.
- Component files: PascalCase (e.g., `UserCard.tsx`).
- Prefer named exports over default exports.

## Task Context
This project is orchestrated by orai. Task files are in `.agents/tasks/`.
Do NOT modify files in `.agents/`.
